## Rule: Keep this file updated
Only add files to the list in **docs/project_structure.md** after you have read them wholly. Update descriptions there when files change significantly.

### addons/display_commander (folders)
- audio, autoclick, config, display, dlss, dualsense, dxgi
- hdr_upgrade, hooks (d3d9, dxgi, ddraw, input, nvidia, opengl, vulkan, windows_hooks, wgi)
- input_remapping, latency, latent_sync, nvapi, presentmon, proxy_dll
- res, settings
- ui (new_ui, monitor_settings)
- utils
- widgets (remapping_widget, xinput_widget, resolution_widget, dualsense_widget)
- window_management
- adhd_multi_monitor

### includes
- use ImGui from reshade: <imgui.h>, <reshade.hpp>
- use MinHook for hooks

### not allowed
- std locks aren't allowed
